p.k: This new episode of One day with presents the private life of one of our new Playboy TV Europe models: Ksenia Morozova, from Russia! From the morning, enjoying some time in bed before preparing her breakfast, until the evening, when she models for a sensual shooting session. Ksenia loves outdoor activities so she’s constantly on the move! And you are invited to witness all her sport activities: a stretching session, a kart race and a soccer practicing with the women’s local team. In the end, a promenade by Tula, her favorite city in the world – and where she actually leaves. So come with us and don’t miss anything from her everyday life!
